This directory contains a test environment for experimenting with splitting algorithms.


References for efficient algorithms


Line segment intersections:

De Berg, M., van Kreveld, M., Overmars, M. ja Schwarzkopf, O:
"Chapter 2: Line segment intersection", Computational Geometry (2nd
ed.), Springer-Verlag, pp. 19–44, ISBN 978-3-540-65620-3, 2000.

Polygon splitting:

Wu, L., Tian, G. ja Xie, Z.: An algorithm for splitting arbitrary
polygon, Natural Computation, 2009. ICNC'09. Fifth International
Conference on Natural Computation, 6, 318–325, 2009.
